# =========================
# Important Notes:
# =========================
# 1. Never commit .env files containing sensitive data
# 2. Always use environment variables for API keys
# 3. Exclude uploaded files from version control
# 4. Keep test files separate from production data
# 5. Regular security audits of committed files
# ========================= 